Rooms.Name: The First Circle
Rooms.Description: You standing on a large, flat plane. A wall looms before you to the west.

Rooms.Name: The Gates of Hell
Rooms.Description: You stand before a massive wall constructed of stone. In the center, a massive gate blocks you way to the north.

Rooms.Name: On The Shores of the Lake of Fire
Rooms.Description: The shore is littered with the wreckage of ships. Fires burn from their hulls as thousands of souls cry out.

Rooms.Name: The Clouds
Rooms.Description: You are floating, weightless, amongst clouds. Everything is foggy, and amorphous shapes swirl around you.

Rooms.Name: The Pearly Gates
Rooms.Description: You stand before massive golden gates. The sound of music played by harps fills your ears.

Rooms.Name: Crypticant's Room
Rooms.Description: You are in a cubic room floating through time and space.
